{"tid":1996200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"河北多人燒「潔淨煤」中毒亡。  官方：煤和爐具品質合格","createTime":"2020-04-30T20:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T23:53:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":239,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"a43d9a18cf78da2143655020792f8941dd831046","tid":1996200,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T20:16:42.000Z","msg":"【河北多人燒「潔淨煤」中毒亡】<br />\n【官方：煤和爐具品質合格】<br />\n<br />\n河北政府去年出於環保考慮，強制民眾棄用散煤，改以「潔淨煤」取暖，但之後各地相繼有人燃燒「潔淨煤」後一氧化碳中毒身亡，更有醫院一天接收30多位一氧化碳中毒患者。<br />\n<br />\n唐山有村民指，改用「潔淨煤」的第一天，23歲的兒子就在睡夢中離世，發現時嘴角流血、有沫，法醫口頭稱「八成是煤氣中毒」。但由於沒有正式驗屍報告，村委拒賠償，「先頭說給我解決，後來改口說沒有證據」。<br />\n<br />\n當地政府落村排查後，指「潔淨煤」和爐具質量合格，但要求加強爐具通風設施，並加裝一氧化碳警報器。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2526524874158650/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2526524874158650%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=ef7befec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2526524874158650/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"86023312bdf5c1236f049f30d0367170d1e47e7d","tid":1996200,"uid":46245,"like":328,"dislike":2,"score":326,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T20:22:10.000Z","msg":"官方；「潔淨煤」當然合格，不過你班窮人唔合格姐"},{"pid":"9d01b92355a551b81084358274a8d23191a3918f","tid":1996200,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T20:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323b1941d5306b9aea9e89edb6e938639463a93c","tid":1996200,"uid":224561,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T20:29:38.000Z","msg":"好似上年年尾先見到呢啲新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c6bae0d15e510bb7e6377c5825a8f7829767e6","tid":1996200,"uid":99402,"like":162,"dislike":1,"score":161,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T20:29:53.000Z"